reviewText: Being a Wallace Beery fan, I enjoyed it very much. Wish I could find his movie ""20 Mule-team"
jackass mail another great movie with Wallace Beery from 1942 with Marjorie Main they made a great movie team jackass mail is one of there best.

Great movie, nostalgic memories. There is only one Wallace Beery! Marjorie Main is great too. Good old western with tried and true Beery formula. He plays outlaw who turns hero, in spite of his efforts to be an outlaw.
